    "scent_blocks_2_Gd87YR": {
      "type": "scent-blocks-2",
      "blocks": {
        "image_J9mQBq": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "width": "w-90",
            "layout": false,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_4_800x_png.png",
            "mimage": "shopify://shop_images/Group_2_800x_png.png",
            "scent_heading": "Patchouli & Cedarwood",
            "heading-position": false,
            "scent_details": "<p> <b class=\"value\"> Refreshing &amp; Relaxing\n <b></b> </b></p> A captivating, rich bouquet of warm woody notes of red cedar and amyris perfectly complemented by the distinctive, earthy and sweet tones of patchouli. The Intense lemony aroma of May Chang adds a sparkling, fresh, sherbet-like twist to this moth-deterring blend.",
            "infoHeading": "Note Information",
            "infoDetails": "<p class=\"value-bold blue-text\">Top Notes</p><p>Fresh, juicy May Chang reminds us of a joyful lemon sorbet</p>\n<p class=\"value-bold blue-text\">Middle Notes</p>\n<p>Sweet Palmarosa is grassy and earthy getting us in the mood for a spring walk</p>\n<p class=\"value-bold blue-text\">Base Notes</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Red Cedarwood is the star of this concentrate, as its sweet, balsamic scent has the ability to cover the smell of keratin, which moths love!</li>\n<li>Deep and distinctive, herbaceous Patchouli gives this concentrate its rich, woody and slightly sweet aroma</li>\n</ul>"
          }
        },
        "image_r9gEdH": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "width": "w-80",
            "layout": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_3_10ac8ca3-7f22-4f75-912e-0bc0ed86770e_800x_png.png",
            "mimage": "shopify://shop_images/Group_1_800x_png.png",
            "scent_heading": "Lemon & Marjoram",
            "heading-position": false,
            "scent_details": "<p> <b class=\"value-bold\"> Zingy &amp; Zesty </b> </p>\nA spray of this exclusive scent will transport you to a fresh Mediterranean kitchen, with notes of lush greens, sweet, woody marjoram and vibrant lemon, it’s the perfect welcome to Spring.",
            "infoHeading": "Note Information",
            "infoDetails": "<p class=\"value-bold blue-text\">Top Notes</p><p>Light, sharp and fresh, this lemony scent has us feeling uplifted and ready for spring</p>\n<p class=\"value-bold blue-text\">Middle Notes</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Sweet marjoram adds warm, delicately floral notes</li>\n<li>\nClary sage is distinctive and sweet, with herbaceous and earthy hints \n</li>\n<li>Palmarosa adds sweetness, as well as grassy and earthy undertones</li>\n</ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "image_J9mQBq",
        "image_r9gEdH"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "heading": "Discover our limited edition Spring scents",
        "subheading": ""
      }
    },
    "11e26e64-5410-48f9-9c9a-3698a74d1770": {
      "type": "two-women-2",
      "custom_css": [
        ".blue-text {color: #2d469e !important;}"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "className": "two-women-wrapper-2",
        "background": "",
        "layout": false,
        "main_heading": "Two women on a mission",
        "sub_heading": "Best friends Charlotte Figg and Purdy Rubin got together to create natural cleaning products that are powerful, \n <br>safe and inspired by beautiful seasonal scents.",
        "heading": "",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/c0855ba36e497bb2acf6ef7605222d4a.jpg",
        "details": "<div class=\"value-sans\">\n<p class=\"blue-text value-medium\">Fed up with unpleasant, highly toxic cleaning products, the two friends decided to do something about it.\n\n</p>\n<span class=\"gray-text\">They both firmly believe in the power and joy of natural cleaning, so they started experimenting with formulas in their garage. It's there that they conjured up their multi-surface cleaner infused with pure essential oils.\n</span>\n</div>"
      }
    },
